'''Aro''' was a small [[Droid/Legends|droid]] manufacturer founded by [[Lirran Aro]]. It was based in the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]] and produced security droids. It was later learned that [[Aro-GX Security Droid]]s had been reprogrammed to [[Assassin/Legends|assassinate]] a noted [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] official, which forced Aro to declare bankruptcy when they were hit with bad publicity and a huge drop in sales.<ref name="CFTD" />

